members.description: The Royale Compiler will inject script elements into the index.html file.  Surround with "inject_script" tag as follows:  <inject_script> var link = document.createElement("link"); link.setAttribute("rel", "stylesheet"); link.setAttribute("type", "text/css"); link.setAttribute("href", "http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.2/themes/smoothness/jquery-ui.css"); document.head.appendChild(link); var script = document.createElement("script"); script.setAttribute("src", "http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.1.js"); document.head.appendChild(script); script = document.createElement("script"); script.setAttribute("src", "http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.2/jquery-ui.js"); document.head.appendChild(script); </inject_script>
